&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Prescribing Support Technician - Band 5&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Fixed Term positions – Full Time/Part Time hours&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Permanent position – Part Time hours&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting opportunity to join a dynamic team of practice based pharmacy technicians offering medicines management support to Primary Care Networks and their member Practices. The successful candidate must be adaptable, friendly, self-motivated and enjoy working in a challenging and changing environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The team work closely with individual practices to ensure safe prescribing practice, formulary adherence and implementation of best practice guidance in addition to more general support to the wider practice team and members of the public.&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
